| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1424 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6770eb0b-4c13-5a9c-8e71-54d56e7100c5"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
